```python
lat = df["Latitude"].values
long = df["Longitude"].values

Name = df["Name"].values
Location = df["Location"].values
Country = df["Country"].values
```


```python
for i in range(len(df)):    
    x.add_child(fo.Marker(location=[lat[i],long[i]],popup=Name[i]+"\n"+Location[i]+"\n"+Country[i],icon=fo.Icon(color='darkred')))
```


```python
bMap.add_child(x)
```
